 Instruccions to install Colemak Keyboard
 
 1. Make a backup of /usr/share/X11/xkb/symbols/us
 
 2. Replace it with us file
 
 3. Add this line in /usr/share/X11/xkb/rules/xfree86.lst under !variant :
 colemak-prog    us: English (programmer Colemak)
 
 4. Add this in /usr/share/X11/xkb/rules/xfree86.xml
 
<variant>
    <configItem>
        <name>colemak-prog</name>
        <description>English (programmer Colemak)</description>
    </configItem>
</variant>

5. Restart X server (Ctrl-Alt-Backspace)